{"type": "article", "id": 23235, "title": "风靡日本的王将饺子开了一家新店，女顾客会特别喜欢", "description": "还配有各种女性专属菜单：奶酪蒸蔬菜猪肉、蛋糕形状的玉子烧、酸味奶油泡水饺", "date": "2016-03-03T15:27:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 23713, "name": "饺子"}, {"id": 6400, "name": "咖啡店"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}], "category": 18, "author": 474100, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 154, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120139X70LVb5oSNJKDv6U.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">日本王将食品服务公司旗下的连锁店“王将饺子（餃子の王将）”在京都开设了首家由女性团队领导、面向女性顾客的新概念店铺“GYOZA OHSHO 鸟丸御池店”。该店已于 3 月 3 日正式开张。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120133v8orBVsGQdu0ZezX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64117647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">这个风靡日本的有名中华料理店一直很受国民欢迎，可是据店铺统计，男女顾客比例大约是 8:2，女顾客数量极少。这次为吸引 20 到 39 岁的女性顾客，王将使出浑身解数，“从外到内”进行了一次变革。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120134A2GaUYEZCLltf7iS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59693878\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">普通连锁店长这样</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120134dlTyBsHbAxGIuQ54.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">新店长这样</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">和之前连锁店的传统日式装修相比，这家新店走起了时尚的咖啡店风格，在考虑今后进军国际的基础上，以“日式休闲”为主要理念，采用女设计师的设计。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120135sjxSlcFY21dgnzLe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120135CzwybSxUJlG7HKeQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120135MnPLwcjGdTXg7oY0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021201367p3lLHSrfBVKPbyA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66612903\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">店铺外设置了木质感的高脚桌，内部装修也大量使用木材。店内前方做成“吧台风”，打造开放式空间，另设有半包厢，为顾客提供了轻松安静的空间，同时又兼具热闹感和舒适感，试图给女性顾客带来清洁、温暖的感受。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120136xV2R9D4kMYEWwoQq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">在厨房设备上，采用全新的“干燥式厨房”，通过让水不流到地板的设计保证厨房卫生。开放式阳台设有能站着用餐的区域，全面考虑女性顾客的就餐体验。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">新店还请来女性料理研究家开发各种新的健康菜色，一般的王将店主要以煎饺、拉面、八宝饭为主，但这次推出的新菜单几乎全是女性顾客喜欢的口味。比如奶酪蒸蔬菜和猪肉、蛋糕状的玉子烧、酸味奶油泡水饺等低热量限定菜品，搭配杏仁豆腐、葡萄酒和鸡尾酒，种类还算丰富。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021201372AKHzwP04hnip8bd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">普通连锁店内的蛋炒饭和煎饺</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120137YAm63yTa0z8bvuBN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66612903\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">新店的酸味奶油泡水饺</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120138DLholQFHTr8GZKkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66612903\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">奶酪蒸蔬菜和猪肉</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120138kvHJ6YKeqLNlg59f.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66612903\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">蛋糕状的玉子烧</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120139fgwYbaGKIPM15zc4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">杏仁豆腐</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">这只是一个开端，王将打算逐渐把这类新式连锁店开到全日本，有可能的话还要再次进军海外市场。</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图来自 <a href=\"http://www.favy.jp/topics/4907\">favy</a> </p>\n\n"}